	<name>GetIt</name>
	<summary>Send HTTP requests to API endpoints</summary>
	<translation type="gettext">getit</translation>

	<description>
		<p>
			GetIt&#39;s main focus is to make your life a lot easier when you have to test APIs or use somebody elses API.
			We know it can be hard to find a great, simple and open source application for this task that&#39;s not command
			line based.
		</p>
		<p>
			Features of GetIt include:
		</p>

		<ul>
			<li>sending HTTP requests to API endpoints and display the response of the server</li>
			<li>saving and opening requests</li>
			<li>easily open recent saved/opened requests</li>
			<li>sending custom POST data</li>
			<li>syntax highlighting</li>
			<li>Preview for HTML response</li>
			<li>Make JSON response look beautifull automatically</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

	<launchable type="desktop-id">net.bartkessels.getit.desktop</launchable>

